{"tid":747682,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記後防一直以嚟都俾人低估咗","createTime":"2018-07-18T14:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T02:47:01.000Z","uid":144513,"like":39,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"97c15219b0a4b43a5c35606c57fce64e8fd907c2","tid":747682,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"想忘記卡利奧斯嘅錯 <br />\n唯有懷緬下以前嘅光輝歲月<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n射得咁&quot;衡&quot;拉爾拿都咁有膽識去嘗試接實<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/221258_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F221258_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=26759ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶刀侍衛除咗艾加之外 仲有副隊長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/221259_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F221259_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=065f5b04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n高路托尼都不甘示弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/221306_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F221306_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=19b00080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拳怕少壯?加歷查勇敢挑戰19歲盧卡古<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/221308_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F221308_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=292af589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入侵者都頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/215503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F215503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b155661f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連拿嘅冷靜 一啲都唔似神經刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拼命三郎盧卡斯 努力攔截<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n史卡迪爾同史基泰爾一樣咁硬淨 咬緊牙關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家仲有世界級中堅帶領 喺決賽再接再勵 屢敗屢戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/223145_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F223145_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=425c7d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">利物浦世界第一</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2650fa818a066300549891b434e9580bde0810be","tid":747682,"uid":190213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"Siuchiyin垃撚圾比女飛仲on撚799串9人笑到仆街"},{"pid":"e2cb9cc8309ce89d0226d72e1966924a4b8dceb1","tid":747682,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2650fa818a066300549891b434e9580bde0810be","tid":747682,"uid":190213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"Siuchiyin垃撚圾比女飛仲on撚799串9人笑到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"mk仔死返fb啦